SELECT "api_user"."id", "api_user"."password", "api_user"."last_login", "api_user"."is_superuser", "api_user"."first_name", "api_user"."last_name", "api_user"."is_staff", "api_user"."is_active", "api_user"."date_joined", "api_user"."username", "api_user"."email" FROM "api_user" WHERE "api_user"."id" = 1 LIMIT 21

SELECT "api_chatmessage"."id", "api_chatmessage"."user_id", "api_chatmessage"."sender_id", "api_chatmessage"."reciever_id", "api_chatmessage"."message", "api_chatmessage"."is_read", "api_chatmessage"."date" FROM "api_chatmessage" WHERE "api_chatmessage"."id" IN (SELECT "subquery"."last_msg" FROM (SELECT DISTINCT (SELECT U0."id" FROM "api_chatmessage" U0 WHERE ((U0."reciever_id" = 1 AND U0."sender_id" = (V0."id")) OR (U0."reciever_id" = (V0."id") AND U0."sender_id" = 1)) ORDER BY U0."id" DESC LIMIT 1) AS "last_msg", V0."id" FROM "api_user" V0 LEFT OUTER JOIN "api_chatmessage" V1 ON (V0."id" = V1."sender_id") LEFT OUTER JOIN "api_chatmessage" V3 ON (V0."id" = V3."reciever_id") WHERE (V1."reciever_id" = 1 OR V3."sender_id" = 1) ORDER BY V0."id" DESC) subquery) ORDER BY "api_chatmessage"."id" DESC
